plot: Jeana takes Kimberly and Scott house hunting, then hosts a neighborhood BBQ. Sparks fly as Shane takes an interest in Jo. Kimberly comes clean with Scott about her crazy weekend in Palm Springs. Unhappy that Jo has gone back to work, Slade retaliates by hiring a sexy new assistant. Vicki and her husband Donn argue about Briana's job and Lauri continues to struggle with her children as Ashley fails to show up for work after discovering her car has disappeared.—Anonymous
